title: SHOCK: Beautiful mom of 3 dead from "Brazilian Butt Lift"
itunes:title: SHOCK: Beautiful mom of 3 dead from "Brazilian Butt Lift"
description:
Danea Plascencia, A 28-year-old mother of three young children, is rushed to the hospital -- unresponsive -- after having Brazilian butt lift surgery, a procedure where fat is removed from the body and re-injected into a patient's backside. Will the surgeon face homicide charges?

Nancy's Expert Panel Weighs In:

Vincent Hill   Private Investigator

Dr. Daniel Bober:  Forensic Psychiatrist

Dr. Michelle Dupree:   Medical Examiner

Kenya Johnson:  Atlanta prosecutor

David Mack:   Syndicated Radio Host
